# DepVet environment variables
#
# OPTIONAL. DepVet works fully without this — detection is deterministic
# (OSV + npm + typosquat + scoring). When set, the AI layer adds calm,
# plain-English explanations + prioritization on top of the real findings.
# If unset or the call fails, DepVet renders the deterministic report unchanged.
#
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com  →  set in Vercel project env.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
